# Enterprise Data Engineering Pipeline with Microsoft Fabric

An end-to-end automated data engineering project built on **Microsoft Fabric**, leveraging **Medallion Architecture (Bronze $\rightarrow$ Silver $\rightarrow$ Gold)**, **PySpark**, **T-SQL Warehouse**, and **Data Factory Orchestration**.

---

## Architecture Overview

```text
[ Raw Data Source ]
        │
        ▼
[ Lakehouse (Bronze) ]  ──(PySpark Clean & Transform)──► [ Lakehouse (Silver/Gold) ]
                                                                   │
                                                           (Stored Procedure)
                                                                   ▼
[ Data Factory Pipeline ] ◄──(Scheduled at 02:00 AM)─────── [ Data Warehouse ]
        │                                                          │
        ├──► (On Success) ──► Trigger SQL Procedure                ▼
        └──► (On Failure) ──► Automated Notification       [ Semantic Model & RLS ]
